tical destiny of this country, based largely on demographic shifts, as described in Barack Obama's America." -- Publisher's description.  aDescription based on information from the publisher.10aObama, Barack.10aReagan, Ronald. 0aFamilieszUnited StatesxHistory. 0aCoalitionszUnited StatesxHistory. 0aUnited StatesxSocial conditionsy1980- 4aElectronic books.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher. 0aContemporary political and social issues40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.17422